<bibRefCitation author="Fry, G. C. &amp; Brewer, D. T. &amp; Venables, W. N." box="[876,1054,1628,1653]" pageId="170" pageNumber="171" pagination="126 - 141" refId="ref188009" refString="Fry, G. C., Brewer, D. T. &amp; Venables, W. N. (2006) Vulnerability of deepwater demersal fishes to commercial fishing: Evidence from a study around a tropical volcanic seamount in Papua New Guinea. Fisheries Research, 81, 126 - 141." type="journal article" year="2006">
Fry 
<emphasis box="[922,971,1628,1653]" italics="true" pageId="170" pageNumber="171">et al</emphasis>
. (2006
</bibRefCitation>
: 129); specimens photographed at Kavieng fish market by Barry C. Russell during 
<date box="[695,876,1664,1688]" pageId="170" pageNumber="171" value="2014-06-07" valueMax="2014-06-28" valueMin="2014-06-07">7–28 June 2014</date>
.
</paragraph>
